<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Pro-Level IoT Monitoring</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 30px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px 20px; }
    .pro-badge { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%); color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; }
    .device-count { font-size: 48px; font-weight: bold; color: #667eea; margin: 20px 0; }
    .feature-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 30px 0; }
    .feature-card { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea; }
    .cta-button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 15px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px; }
    .cta-button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3); }
    .step-list { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%); padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 14px; color: #666; }
    .support-highlight { background-color: #e8f4f8; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #17a2b8; margin: 30px 0; }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .feature-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .cta-button { display: block; text-align: center; margin: 10px 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="pro-badge">üöÄ PRO USER</div>
      <h1>Welcome to Pro-Level IoT Monitoring!</h1>
      <div class="device-count"><%= @device_count %></div>
      <p>Devices Ready for Advanced Monitoring</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,</p>

      <p>Congratulations on your pro-level IoT investment! With <strong><%= @device_count %> devices</strong> in your order, you're ready to unlock the full potential of enterprise-grade monitoring and analytics.</p>

      <!-- Advanced Features Grid -->
      <h3>üéØ Your Pro-Level Advantages</h3>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <% @advanced_features.each do |feature| %>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h4><%= feature[:name] %></h4>
            <p><%= feature[:description] %></p>
            <div style="color: #28a745; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;">
              üí° <%= feature[:benefit] %>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Actions -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/device-activation" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
          üîó Activate Your Devices
        </a>
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/dashboard/pro" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
          üìä Access Pro Dashboard
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Next Steps -->
      <div class="step-list">
        <h3>üóìÔ∏è Your Pro Onboarding Roadmap</h3>
        <ol style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
          <% @next_steps.each do |step| %>
            <li style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 16px;"><%= step %></li>
          <% end %>
        </ol>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;"><strong>Estimated completion time:</strong> 45-60 minutes</p>
      </div>

      <!-- ROI Projection -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
        <h3>üìà Your Potential ROI</h3>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin: 15px 0;">Pro users typically see <strong>250-400% ROI</strong> in their first year</p>
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-around; margin: 20px 0;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">85%</div>
            <div>Reduced Downtime</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">$50K+</div>
            <div>Average Savings</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;">2 hrs</div>
            <div>Daily Time Saved</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Support Highlight -->
      <div class="support-highlight">
        <h4>ü§ù Your Pro Support Package</h4>
        <ul style="margin: 15px 0;">
          <% if @support_options[:priority_support] %>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Priority Support</strong> - Skip the queue, get help faster</li>
          <% end %>
          <% if @support_options[:dedicated_onboarding] %>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Dedicated Onboarding</strong> - Personal setup assistance</li>
          <% end %>
          <% if @support_options[:custom_training] %>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Custom Training Session</strong> - One-on-one with our experts</li>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
          <strong>Pro Support Hotline:</strong> 1-800-XSPACE-PRO<br>
          <strong>Priority Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:pro-support@SpaceGrow.com">pro-support@SpaceGrow.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Advanced Resources -->
      <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h4>üìö Pro Resources & Training</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/getting-started">Pro User Quick Start Guide</a></li>
          <li><a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/api-docs">Complete API Documentation</a></li>
          <li><a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/best-practices">Multi-Device Best Practices</a></li>
          <li><a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/case-studies">Enterprise Case Studies</a></li>
          <li><a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/webinars">Exclusive Pro Webinar Series</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Access -->
      <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffeaa7 0%, #fab1a0 100%); padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin: 30px 0;">
        <h3>üë• Join the Pro Community</h3>
        <p>Connect with other pro users, share insights, and get exclusive tips from our engineering team.</p>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 15px;">
          <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/community/pro" class="cta-button" style="color: white;">
            üåü Access Pro Community
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
        You've made an excellent investment in your monitoring infrastructure. We're here to ensure you get maximum value from every device.<br><br>
        <strong>Welcome to the pro level!</strong><br>
        The SpaceGrow Pro Team
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        SpaceGrow Pro ‚Ä¢ Enterprise IoT Monitoring<br>
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro">Pro Dashboard</a> ‚Ä¢ 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/support">Pro Support</a> ‚Ä¢ 
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.config.app_host %>/pro/resources">Pro Resources</a>
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 12px; margin-top: 15px;">
        Order #<%= @order.id %> ‚Ä¢ <%= @device_count %> devices ‚Ä¢ Pro onboarding initiated
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: 11px; margin-top: 10px;">
        <a href="<%= unsubscribe_url(@unsubscribe_token) %>">Unsubscribe from marketing emails</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>